even more enticing!<!-- notionvc: e938c0ee-5719-47f8-82cb-315f05f3f5b1 --><=
/p>
<p>Flirt Profiles can contain up to 7,000 characters, while Listings can co=
ntain up to 14,000 characters. To ensure the best viewing experience for yo=
ur customers, please keep in mind the standard widths for devices:</p>
<ul>
<li>375px (smartphone)</li>
<li>800px (tablet)</li>
<li>1075px (desktop)</li>
</ul>
<p>If you prefer a fixed width for your Flirt Profile, we recommend using 8=
00px for a consistent look across devices. For Listings, maximum width is 8=
20px.<br><br></p>
<p>Jump ahead to:</p>
